                    <p>We would like to thank you for visitng our website and, while you're here, we'd like to tell you a little about McKelvey Designs.</p>
                    <p>We are Ron and Debbie McKelvey and McKelvey Designs is our family business. We started McKelvey Designs in 1991 after having worked with my parents and grandparents in our family business for 20 years. Hull-McKelvey Beauti-Pleat Draperies was a large, well known drapery business that covered the windows in many homes throughout Houston and the surrounding areas during Houston's building boom from the 60's until the oil bust in the eighties. At Hull-McKelvey, we worked with Perry Homes, General Homes, Village Builders, US Homes, and other builders by decorating model homes and providing drapes and blinds for their offices, "spec" houses, and their personal homes. We received quite an education in business and the home decorating field during that time. Debbie got her education in interior design at the University of Houston and Southwest Texas State University.</p>
